        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="部署到Cloud-Studio"><a href="#部署到Cloud-Studio" class="headerlink" title="部署到Cloud Studio"></a>部署到Cloud Studio</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 新建、编写</span></span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> /home/coding/workspace/blog &amp;&amp; sudo hexo n <span class="string">"My New Post"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 发布并备份</span></span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> /home/coding/workspace/blog &amp;&amp; sudo hexo clean &amp;&amp; sudo hexo g &amp;&amp; sudo hexo d \</span><br><span class="line">  &amp;&amp; sudo git add .. &amp;&amp; sudo git commit -m <span class="string">"new"</span> &amp;&amp; sudo git push origin backup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a>]]></content>
      
      
